libclocale
------------------------------------------
libclocale is a library for cross-platform C locale functions.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.4-2
  libcerror1-20220101-1bl1
  libclocale-devel-20220107-1bl2
  libclocale1-20220107-1bl2
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-2
  cygport-0.34.2-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  libcerror-devel-20220101-1bl1
  libtool-2.4.6-8
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libyal/libclocale

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/libyal/libclocale/archive/refs/tags/20220107.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libclocale-20220107-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libclocale-20220107-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libclocale-20220107-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libclocale-20220107-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libclocale1-20220107-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libclocale-devel-20220107-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libclocale)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libclocale.README
  /usr/share/doc/libclocale/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libclocale/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libclocale/COPYING.LESSER
  /usr/share/doc/libclocale/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libclocale/README

(libclocale1)
  /usr/bin/cygclocale-1.dll

(libclocale-devel)
  /usr/include/libclocale.h
  /usr/include/libclocale/definitions.h
  /usr/include/libclocale/error.h
  /usr/include/libclocale/extern.h
  /usr/include/libclocale/features.h
  /usr/include/libclocale/types.h
  /usr/lib/libclocale.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libclocale.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/libclocale.3.gz

